Project Summary

Project Information

FieldValue
NameFitNesse Launcher Parent
DescriptionProvides ability to launch FitNesse as a wiki server, or automatically run FitNesse tests as part of a standard integration-test / verify build. Allows configuration of FitNesse's classpath through plugin dependencies, and injects all Maven project properties as FitNesse variables, ( which can be overridden from the command line using '-D' ).
Homepagehttp://code.google.com/p/fitnesse-launcher-maven-plugin
